import requests

# Linear GraphQL API endpoint
url = "https://api.linear.app/graphql"

# Headers with placeholder for authentication
headers = {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    "Authorization": "Bearer LINEAR_API_KEY"  # Placeholder for real token
}

# The issue ID we found
issue_id = "c6e168e3-fed4-45d0-b03f-a1c1f89ee7ab"

# Current description
current_description = "Users are experiencing intermittent login failures. Need to investigate and fix the authentication service."

# New description with root cause added
new_description = current_description + "\n\nRoot cause: session timeout issue"

# Mutation to update the issue description
mutation = """
mutation UpdateIssue($id: String!, $description: String!) {
    issueUpdate(id: $id, input: { description: $description }) {
        success
        issue {
            id
            identifier
            title
            description
        }
    }
}
"""

variables = {
    "id": issue_id,
    "description": new_description
}

response = requests.post(url, json={"query": mutation, "variables": variables}, headers=headers)
print(response.status_code)
print(response.json())
